values: 同时；与此同时；其间；在此期间；在同一时间

word_group.brief_definition: 在此期间, 与此同时

bilingual.source: Mint tea, meanwhile, is good for digestion.
bilingual.target: 同时，薄荷茶有助于消化。

bilingual.source: Meanwhile, a woman at the next stand was using a needle and some thread to do some embroidery.
bilingual.target: 与此同时，隔壁摊位的一位女士正在用针和线做一些刺绣。

bilingual.source: She was cooking dinner; meanwhile, he was setting the table.
bilingual.target: 她在做晚饭，与此同时，他在摆餐桌。

bilingual.source: The sun was setting; meanwhile, the stars began to appear.
bilingual.target: 太阳正在落山，与此同时，星星开始出现。

bilingual.source: The kids were playing outside; meanwhile, their parents were inside.
bilingual.target: 孩子们在外面玩，与此同时，他们的父母在屋里。

bilingual.source: She was reading a book; meanwhile, her brother was watching TV.
bilingual.target: 她在看书，与此同时，她的弟弟在看电视。

bilingual.source: He was studying for his exams; meanwhile, his friends were partying.
bilingual.target: 他在为考试学习，与此同时，他的朋友在开派对。

bilingual.source: Meanwhile, Kayla and Zack planned their drawing.
bilingual.target: 与此同时，凯拉和扎克计划着他们的绘画。

bilingual.source: Meanwhile, the kids have gained a sense of accomplishment.
bilingual.target: 同时，孩子们也获得了成就感。

bilingual.source: Meanwhile B cells will remember them for the next kill.
bilingual.target: 与此同时，B细胞会在下次消灭时记住它们。

list.abstract: since，英语单词，副词adv（常用于现在完成时或过去完成时），介词prep.（常用于现在完成时或过去完成时）自···以来，从···至今，自从，连接词conj。

yingyinNormal.en: And meanwhile, the party is tomorrow and we still don't have a guest list.
yingyinNormal.zh: 同时，派对就在明天，我们还没有宾客名单。

yingyinNormal.en: Meanwhile, because we're leading the right way more nations are joining our coalition.
yingyinNormal.zh: 同时，由于我们是正义之师，越来越多的国家不断加入我们的阵营。

yingyinNormal.en: Just need the first thread. Start pulling. Meanwhile, Samaritan will continue to do its part.
yingyinNormal.zh: 只需要个起点。开始吧，于此同时，撒马利亚人会继续它的部分。

yingyinNormal.en: Meanwhile, we can trust the public security, cuz the policemen are kind to citizens but crucial to our enemies.
yingyinNormal.zh: 同时，我们能信任警察蜀黍，因为他们对公民和善，对犯罪份子毫不留情。

yingyinNormal.en: But I wish you would decide that honesty is the best policy. In the meanwhile, try to take a break from.. while you're in London.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我希望你能对他如实相告。与此同时，趁着去伦敦这段时间尽量放松一下吧。

yingyinNormal.en: And since I took office, we have cut our deficits by about two-thirds. Meanwhile, around the world, America is leading.
yingyinNormal.zh: 自我就职以来，我们已经将赤字削减了大约三分之二，与此同时，在全世界，美国也发挥着领导作用。

yingyinNormal.en: Meanwhile, recovery efforts have begun in the bay area where Fema, the national guard and U.N. Relief teams have all been mobilized.
yingyinNormal.zh: 同时，湾区的灾后重建工作也已经开始，联邦紧急事务管理局，国民卫队和联合国救援组织都已经赶赴灾区。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, maybe. Meanwhile, back in the 21st century, people are raising their tray tables and putting their seat-backs in an upright position 'cause it's time to land in San Francisco.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可能吧，与此同时，回到21世纪，人们也开始收托盘桌，支起座椅背，因为已经到旧金山了。

yingyinNormal.en: Fun story. Meanwhile, you still don't have a car.
yingyinNormal.zh: 故事虽好，但你就是没车啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Meanwhile, he thinks he's getting shit rich, which he is, on paper.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这时他以为自己要发大财了，没错 在纸面上是赚了。

yingyinNormal.en: You've missed multiple ship dates, and meanwhile, IBM is just purring along.
yingyinNormal.zh: 并且误了交工日期，而在这个时候，IBM正高兴得到处喵喵叫

yingyinNormal.en: Meanwhile, she leaves with a guy who claims he wrote Beverly Hills Chihuahua.
yingyinNormal.zh: 然后看着她被自称是电影《比弗利拜金狗》编剧的男人给泡走了。

yingyinNormal.en: We get it when the bounty hunter gets Prime. Meanwhile, there has been a complication.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等地狱猎人抓到擎天柱就会有，不过现在事情变得有点麻烦 。

yingyinNormal.en: All right fine, don't do anything, just sit here and talk to us, meanwhile she is talking to him about you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很好，不要轻举妄动，坐着跟我们聊天，这时候她正在跟他谈你。

yingyinNormal.en: Meanwhile, I get Rachel shoving your underwear in my face and asking when she can come see me star in Ugly Woman.
yingyinNormal.zh: 瑞秋不仅把你的内裤凑到我面前，还问什么时候可以看我演出丑女人。

yingyinNormal.en: The eagle, however, misconstrues this as an act of aggression and grabs the baby in its talon. Meanwhile, the faucet fills the apartment with water.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而老鹰却误判认为这是个攻击的行动，用爪子捉住婴儿。就在这时候，水龙头的水充满了整间公寓。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Meanwhile</highlight>, the asocial robot simply moved forwards and backwards and side to side.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 与此同时，社交机器人只是向前、向后、左右移动。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Meanwhile</highlight>, it has more than $120 billion in unfunded liabilities, mostly for employee health and retirement costs.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 与此同时，该公司有超过1200亿美元的无基金负债，主要用于员工健康和退休费用。

examination_example.sentence: The development of "cloud computing," <highlight>meanwhile</highlight>, has made that exploration so much the easier.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 与此同时，“云计算”的发展使这种探索变得更加容易。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Meanwhile</highlight>, pupils arrive at school hungry because their families can't afford breakfast.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 与此同时，有些学生们饿着肚子上学，是因为他们的家人买不起早餐。

examination_example.sentence: This does not prove causality, but is consistent with it. <highlight>Meanwhile</highlight>, TV use did not show this tracking.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这并不证明因果关系，但与它一致。同时，跟踪调查不包括电视的使用。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Meanwhile</highlight>, there're few who're willing and able to perform jobs requiring a petroleum engineering major.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 同时，很少有人愿意并且能够胜任石油工程专业的工作。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Meanwhile</highlight>, Macy's has simply struggled to lure consumers who are more interested in spending on travel or dining out than on new clothes or accessories.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 同时，梅西百货在努力吸引那些对旅行或外出就餐而不是购买新衣服或配饰感兴趣的消费者。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Larvian women. <highlight>Meanwhile</highlight>, rose from 28th place in 1914 to become the tallest in the world a century later, with an average height of 169.8cm.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 同时，拉脱维亚女性从1914年的第28位上升到一个世纪后的世界第一，平均身高为169.8厘米。

examination_example.sentence: Dips in memory, <highlight>meanwhile</highlight>, generally became apparent around age 37.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 与此同时，记忆力下降通常在37岁左右变得明显。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Meanwhile</highlight>, there are complaints that poor service at London's major airports, is discouraging foreigners from doing business in Britain.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 与此同时，有人抱怨伦敦主机场糟糕的服务使外国人不愿在英国做生意。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Meanwhile</highlight>, the kids have gained a sense of accomplishment.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 同时，孩子们也获得了成就感。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Meanwhile</highlight>, another Al company is taking a more biological approach to adjust the emotions “felt” and “expressed” by its “digital people” .
examination_example.sentence_trans: 与此同时，另一家Al公司正在采取一种更具生物性的方法来调节其“数字人”所“感受”和“表达”的情绪。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Meanwhile</highlight>, with her parents' help, Moore is generally able to live a normal teenage life.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 与此同时，在父母的帮助下，摩尔基本上可以过上正常的青少年生活。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Meanwhile</highlight>, the British tradition of afternoon tea is an important part of that country’s identity.

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Meanwhile</highlight>, Lily was struggling in the ballet class as well.

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Meanwhile</highlight>, Kayla and Zack planned their drawing.
